==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: dysfunctional
<hw>dysfunctional</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>impaired in
function; especially of a bodily system or organ.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Psychol.)</fld> <def>failing to serve an adjustive
purpose; -- of a trait or condition; <as>as, <ex>dysfunctional</ex>
behavior</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> nonadaptive.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dysgenesic</ent>⟦br⟧
